article.description: — Yacine Toumi's 17 points helped Evansville defeat Illinois State 58-54 on Saturday.
article.headline: Toumi has 17, Evansville beats Illinois State 58-54
article.linkText: Toumi has 17, Evansville beats Illinois State 58-54
article.story: EVANSVILLE, Ind. -- — Yacine Toumi's 17 points helped Evansville defeat Illinois State 58-54 on Saturday. Toumi added six rebounds for the Purple Aces (12-9, 3-7 Missouri Valley Conference). Joshua Hughes scored 11 points, going 5 of 8 (1 for 3 from 3-point range). Tanner Cuff was 3 of 7 shooting and 4 of 5 from the free throw line to finish with 10 points, while adding six rebounds. Darius Burford led the way for the Redbirds (10-11, 4-6) with 18 points. Myles Foster added 12 points for Illinois State. Johnny Kinziger also put up 10 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
